Package: hsquared
Title: R Interface for Julia-Backed Quantitative-Genetic Models
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shinichi", "Nakagawa", , "itchyshin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the R-facing interface for an open quantitative-genetic
    modelling system backed by the HSquared.jl Julia engine. Version 0.1 fits
    the univariate Gaussian animal model (y ~ fixed + animal(1 | id, pedigree =
    ped)) by restricted maximum likelihood and returns heritability, variance
    components, breeding values, and standard extractors. Fitting requires a
    local Julia and HSquared.jl. Genomic, single-step, SNP-BLUP, repeatability,
    two-effect, and multivariate animal models also fit through opt-in,
    experimental engine paths; factor-analytic and non-Gaussian models are
    planned.
